---
import ourCraftIcon from '../assets/our-craft.svg';
import MuppyBento from './MuppyBento.astro';
import Step from './Step.astro';
import Steps from './Steps.astro';
import TrufarioBento from './TrufarioBento.astro';
---

<section id="ai-policy" class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center bg-ash/80 px-6 xl:mt-32 w-full py-16 xl:py-40">
  <div class="flex flex-col center mb-4 xl:mb-10">
    <h1
      class="font-round8 text-center text-white italic xl:text-start xl:text-12xl text-[26vw] leading-22 xl:leading-44"
    >
      Made by
      <br />
      <span class="text-sasquatch-socks xl:ml-20">humans</span>
    </h1>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-2xl xl:text-4xl font-thin text-white text-start mt-16 xl:mt-20 max-w-2xl font-claim">
      <p>
        We are conscious of the negative impact AI is having on our society: the damage to our environment, the
        atrophy to own critical thinking, and the financial implications.
      </p>

      <p>
        They promised AI would revolutionise the tech world. In reality, productivity is arguably the same, thousands of
        people have been fired to increase token budgets, and we still see the same mediocre ideas over and over
        again.
      </p>

      <p>
        In Antropia, we have vowed to minimize our use of AI, and always limit it to certain narrowly-scoped uses. We do
        this because we know the best products are conceived through human connection.
      </p>

      <p>
        We want to continue working with other fellow humans, to learn from them, to understand their problems, and
        to collaborate to find a solution we can be proud of, together.
      </p>

      <p>
        That's why everything we do in Antropia is made by humans. Accountable and proud humans.
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl xl:text-2xl">
        If you want to read more about how we use AI, you can read our <a
        href="https://antropia.studio/blog/ai-manifesto/" class="underline-base hover:decoration-sasquatch-socks">AI
        manifesto</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
